descp2: integer, optional (default=2) Parameter for the Minkowski metric from :class:`sklearn.metrics.pairwise_distances`. When p = 1, this is equivalent to using manhattan_distance (l1), and euclidean_distance (l2) for p = 2. For arbitrary p, minkowski_distance (l_p) is used.
